    <p>
      While many of the projects I've worked on haven't required formal design systems (or haven't had budgets for them), I do strive to design with an eye toward consistency and clarity. One of my favorite UI projects was the Heavybit Industries website design, which is largely <a href="https://www.heavybit.com/" target="_blank">still in use today</a>. I designed every template on the site, working with their talented frontend dev to bring the mocks to life.
    </p>
