      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>
      I'm glad I chose to wholesale these products, as working directly with retailers is a great way to get real feedback&mdash;the analytics of print design. My favorite "analytics" are photos of beaming kiddos with their passport sticker pages filled out! We donate a portion of the profits to local trail groups and offer scores of "duds" to addiction recovery programs.
    </p>
